FBIS4-37128 "drnes117_n_94007" FBIS-NES-94-117 Daily Report 17 Jun 1994 LEBANON Al-Hariri's Illness Causes Cancellation of Meetings Al-Hariri's Illness Causes Cancellation of Meetings NC1706100194 Kafr Killa Voice of the South in Arabic 0930 GMT 17 Jun 94 NC1706100194 Kafr Killa Voice of the South Arabic BFN [Text] Prime Minister Rafiq al-Hariri canceled his appointments yesterday afternoon because he was indisposed. He was feeling pain, which was caused by a past surgical operation in which his kidney was removed. President Ilyas al-Hirawi telephoned al-Hariri to inquire about his health.
